		<description>An anima-touched palm. It lacks the psychic potency of a true anima tree, but still hums faintly with psychic life.\n\nPlant details: Anima palms are wild plants that cannot be cultivated, and they need minimum terrain fertility of 0.05. They can be harvested for wood.</description>
