	<ThingDef ParentName="PlantBase">
		<defName>AB_DesertBouquet</defName>
		<label>desert bouquet</label>
		<description>A spiny plant with some unusual fleshy tentacles sprouting from the top. Seems to be a variation of the blood bouquet found in ocular forests, but the fruit is inedible.\n\nPlant details: Desert bouquet is a wild plant that cannot be cultivated, and it needs minimum terrain fertility of 0.05.</description>
